OL,5,Cconcern
OL,7,FUTV understands that a small number of
OL,8,Fbiomedical scientists have been
OL,9,Freferred to their regulator after
OL,10,Fconcerns were raised about their
OL,11,Ffitness to practice.
OL,13,FIt follows a major review into
OL,14,Fcervical screening in the Southern
OL,15,FTrust, which has led to the recall of
OL,16,Fmore than 17 thousand smear test
OL,17,Fresults.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
