OL,5,Cconcern
OL,7,FSome of the women affected referred
OL,8,Fthe matter to The Health and Care
OL,9,FProfessions Council, and they've
OL,10,Fexpressed anger having heard that the
OL,11,FTrust itself hadn't done so - due to
OL,12,Fwhat the Trust described as
OL,13,F'insufficient information'.
OL,15,FHeather Thompson and Tracey Bell are
OL,16,Ftwo of the women who are part of the
OL,17,Fmajor review into cervical screening
OL,18,Fin the Southern Trust.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
