OL,7,FFortunately they both received the all
OL,8,Fclear but only after months of anxious
OL,9,Fwaiting.
OL,11,FThe recall of the results of more than
OL,12,F17,000 women was announced last
OL,13,FOctober after the intervention of a
OL,14,Fwhistleblower and then a report by the
OL,15,Froyal college of pathologists which
OL,16,Fidentified significant failings in the
OL,17,Flaboratory as far back as 2008.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
