OL,5,Cconcern
OL,7,FNow these campaigners - among others -
OL,8,Fknown as ladies with letters - have
OL,9,Fcalled for the screeners involved to
OL,10,Fbe investigated by the body which
OL,11,Fregulates their profession.
OL,13,FOne of those campaigners, Heather
OL,14,FThompson said: "We just felt it was
OL,15,Fvery important to make sure everything
OL,16,Fis being done correctly and it
OL,17,Finspires ladies to go for smear tests,
OL,18,Fwhich are ever so important."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
