OL,7,FThe group are repeating their call for
OL,8,Fa public inquiry and have requested a
OL,9,Fmeeting with the new health minister
OL,10,FMike Nesbitt.
OL,12,FCampaigner Tracey Bell said: "This
OL,13,Fisn't a witch-hunt, this isn't about
OL,14,Fgoing after individuals, it is all
OL,15,Fabout restoring confidence and that
OL,16,Fwomen can be safe."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
