OL,7,FIn today's statement they said that
OL,8,Fwhile they had been in contact with
OL,9,Fthe Health care professions council or
OL,10,FHCPC 'no screeners had been referred
OL,11,Fto the HCPC by the Southern Trust at
OL,12,Fthis time due to what they described
OL,13,Fas' insufficient information' however
OL,14,Fthey added that was being 'kept under
OL,15,Freview' - a move which has angered the
OL,16,Fwomen involved.
