OL,7,FThe HCPC said they do not share
OL,8,Fdetails or information about
OL,9,Findividual cases where there are
OL,10,Fongoing investigations and legal
OL,11,Fprocesses.
OL,13,FThe Southern Trust say their review is
OL,14,Fnow 97 percent complete.
OL,16,FHeather and Tracey may be leading the
OL,17,Ffight but there are many more women
OL,18,Fand their families affected by this
OL,19,Fscandal who are demanding answers.
